Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 老媽就會看出我是家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 借山崎的房間用一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 這就是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達廣...你都看這些東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這樣反而會招來奇妙的誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...老媽已經到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家族構成都記住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我現在沒工夫理你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這次是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒死了 你就讓媽媽看這種房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我現在正在收拾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 不要礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是你的女朋友 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 把這些都裝進垃圾袋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不僅深入單身男子的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還幫忙掃除？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 你都看這些東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是資料 為了製作遊戲...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是別無選擇 身不由己才看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些也是別無選擇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...你媽媽幾點鐘到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 我倒也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這次是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 還有這麼多沒收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來只有用隱藏必殺技了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部窩到閣樓裡蓋上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 不管三七二十一全部扔過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 現在正忙空不出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣算是勉強過關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後蓋上毛巾作偽裝就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 佐藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是空不出手的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩的名片 重做後放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崎 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會 誤會！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似這「誤會」會變成「事實」呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒想到會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好從頭開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別說了 佐藤你看過這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽的傳真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來機場接我...現在拿出來有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是昨天的傳真 是你自己沒發覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我先把怨念物轉移到樓下的垃圾場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬請收拾出一點空間 夠三個人坐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 達廣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是...資料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 都看這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 這個人偶也要扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在門外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬請快點收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 只要打個招呼就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我昨天在重整房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在屋裡還有點亂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就沒打算進你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子一個人獨居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間肯定連落腳的地方都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我看了就忍不住想打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忙了半天究竟有何意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽有點餓 我們去吃中飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 達廣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰中止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽說要出去吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是說...我也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說 你是今天的女主角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽久等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她就是那個...我的...女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...初次見面 我叫中原岬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...小女不才 請媽媽多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛達廣 這麼可愛的女孩子跟你都浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是達廣的媽媽 叫靜枝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 小岬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡如何 價錢適中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店看來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐有三種菜色可供選擇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崎做的名片帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司的電話就是山崎的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算老媽打過去他也會和我口徑一致
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是YS公司 本公司品質優秀 面向世界蓄勢待發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他不露餡 我就能挺過這個難關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小岬來選真是太明智了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您過獎了 我只是查了導遊書而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼可愛的女孩子當我們家媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼媳婦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你們不是在交往嗎 以結婚為前提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 小岬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們有什麼事瞞著媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有騙你啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們巴不得明天就辦喜事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小岬總該知道達廣背上黑痣的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬 你看上了達廣的哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你決定結婚的主要動機是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤外表英俊 工作踏實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有電腦方面...也很強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他方面...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達廣 你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 這樣下去遲早會露餡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有強制地把話題轉向工作方面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡YS公司 本公司品質優秀 面向世界蓄勢待發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是佐藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計不久老媽就會打電話去你那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 請你就這樣做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 不過也不要耽擱我太久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來小岬 你不是直呼達廣的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直喊他佐藤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年輕人流行這樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 因為是在我面前而顯得拘束？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在騙我吧 全部都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友 還有公司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事 我就是佐藤的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司也是真的 他現在負責寫劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們瞞不過我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我和那孩子一起生活了十八年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他拜託小岬幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那孩子本人卻是那種態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直悶悶不樂 所以我就看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在他心中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能原諒自己的謊言\N那孩子從以前就總抱有奇怪的正義感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕佐藤...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有這麼好的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小達 真的是你打碎的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時 我經常因為做了壞事被媽媽罵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每逢事發 我總是嫁禍於別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命為自己辯解 而媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們家孩子打碎的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當那時 我總有種莫名的罪惡感 身心沉重...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大伯走後 我說了真話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起我就發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不再跟媽媽撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能跟小岬聊天 媽媽很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...我...其實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆就不打擾你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來媽媽和朋友約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬 我家的傻小子就這幅德行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還要拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得出來一次 你們享受約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達廣 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 小岬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加什麼油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨說些傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做戲結束了 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照媽媽說的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去那邊走走好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情勢便會有轉機的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤的媽媽真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得怎樣 普普通通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼果然是我更差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連普通都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 還滿...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠太近 被人看見了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會地點？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 這樣子才算是最普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 說什麼轉機 現在很嚴峻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 旁邊還有人居然就...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐...佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口紅？難道是因為我才...？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...岬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓我等到什麼時候 佐藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了兩個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽怎麼還沒打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連超市都沒去 在這裡傻等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態有變 作戰中止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於細節 我回去後向你匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 幾個包子是擺不平我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你 我浪費了一天的寶貴時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還滿好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫長而艱苦的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,350)}第08話 歡迎來到中華街
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到夏天就少不了C70
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看焰火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心甘情願去跳...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎享受夏之日
